  {
    "id": "nl",
    "title": "主流粵語聲母 “n” 與 “l” 轄字表",
    "intro": "本文用於記錄主流粵語聲母“n”和“l”對立時各所轄者，但不包括容易寫出漢字的，如「你」「能」等，此類字聲母大多可由普通話簡單推出。因此，本文主要關注一般不出現在書面語的詞彙。<br>下表中，<b>記音</b>列可能有兩列，此時前一列是綜合音，可忽略；<br>有些詞可能二聲母皆可，本文不置可否。<br><b>字頭</b>列高亮者<b>不</b>代表本字或正字，而只是基於音、義來選出的相對較爲合理的字；併隨後的小號漢字可分別理解爲「優先字形」及「候選字形」；<br><i>斜體者</i>代表該詞可能不出現在現代廣州話中，本文保留作爲參考；<br>以「Ｘ」表記的字頭表示本文未對該詞指定優先字形。",
    "table": {
      "caption": "聲母 “n” 與 “l” 轄字表",
      "headers": ["韻母", "聲調", "聲母", "記音", "字頭", "釋義"],
      "rows": [
        { "cells": [{ "content": "aa", "rowspan": 20 }, { "content": "1", "rowspan": 4 }, { "content": "n", "rowspan": 3, "class": "A" }, { "content": "naa1", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>拏</span><span class='sub'><small>𠸎</small></span>" }, { "content": "①連詞，與：『我～渠食緊飯』；②替，幫：『我～你做』", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "naa1", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>𪐀</span><span class='sub'><small>拏𠸎</small></span>" }, { "content": "①粘貼：～墻紙；②相關連：～更｜～褦", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "naa1", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>𤸻</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "①疤；②補丁", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "l", "class": "B" }, { "content": "laa1" }, { "content": "<b>laa1<br>la1</b>" }, { "content": "<span class='head'>啦</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "語氣詞", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "2", "rowspan": 6 }, { "content": "n", "rowspan": 2, "class": "A" }, { "content": "naa2", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>俹</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "〔～簁〕作事苟且而不精細：你做事可唔可以唔好咁～", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "naa2", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>乸</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "雌性：雞～｜～型(娘娘腔)", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "l", "rowspan": 7, "class": "B" }, { "content": "laa2<br>laai2", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'><small>瀬</small></span>" }, { "content": "遭遇：～嘢(遇上麻煩)", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "laa2", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "抓、抓拿（一隻手拿握不能完全包住的物體）：『～隻蘿蔔』｜『～～埋一䊆』｜『一手～落去，至攞得幾粒花生』", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "laa2", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "①挽起，拉起：～衫袖；②攬，收回，使聚攏：～成一堆", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "laa2", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "皮膚、粘膜、傷口等受強烈刺激或侵蝕而感到疼痛或者體內的絞痛：『我心～住～住』", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "3", "rowspan": 3 }, { "content": "laa3", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i>" }, { "content": "①〔～口〕喫到油炸辛辣食物喉嚨上火想嚥口水的感覺；②〔油～〕油渣；③變味", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "laa3", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>喇</span><span class='sub'><small>嘑嚹</small></span>" }, { "content": "句尾語氣詞", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "laa3", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>罅</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "縫隙，裂痕", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "4", "rowspan": 6 }, { "content": "n", "rowspan": 3, "class": "A" }, { "content": "naa4", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<i><span class='head'>那</span><span class='sub'></span></i>" }, { "content": "地名用字，水田⟨壯語：naz⟩：～坡", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "naa4", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>嗱</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "①豎中指時的附帶嘆詞，表達鄙視；②（對某人）豎中指：『～佢』；③表拒絕否定對方時的語氣詞", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "naa4", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>嗱</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "嘆詞，表指示，引起別人的注意：『～，幾多！』｜『～，睇了喂！』", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "l", "rowspan": 6, "class": "B" }, { "content": "laa4", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>𪢘喇</small></span>" }, { "content": "表示詢問某種情況是否發生：『王伯䎺～？』｜『啲人走澌～？』", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "laa4", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "〔大～～〕數額大：～幾千文", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "laa4", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "〔～～聲〕〔～～臨〕叫別人快點，麻利地：『～清数』", "class": "mean" }] },
        { "cells": [{ "content": "5" }, { "content": "laa5", "colspan": 2 }, { "content": "<span class='head'>藞</span><span class='sub'></span>" }, { "content": "〔～䕢〕髒亂", "class": "mean" }] }
      ]
    }
  },
